          madhane ʿālam</dc:title><dc:title xml:lang="gez">ሰአሊ፡ ለነ፡ ማርያም፡ ሰአሊ፡ ለነ፡ ማርያም፡ ኀበ፡ ወልድኪ፡ ኄር፡ መድኀኔ፡ ዓለም፡</dc:title><crm:P102_has_title rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4960Taabbeyo/title/t1" xml:lang="gez"/><dc:title xml:lang="gez">Saʾali lana Māryām saʾali lana Māryām ḫaba waldǝki ḫer madhane ʿālam</dc:title><dc:title xml:lang="en">Pray for us, Mary, pray for us, Mary, to your Good Son, Saviour of the World...</dc:title><dc:title xml:lang="gez">ተዐብዮ፡ ነፍስየ፡ ለእግዚአብሔር፡</dc:title><crm:P102_has_title rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4960Taabbeyo/title/t2" xml:lang="gez"/><dc:title xml:lang="gez">Taʿabbǝyo nafsǝya la-ʾƎgziʾabǝḥer</dc:title><dc:title xml:lang="en">My soul magnifies God...</dc:title><dcterms:hasPart rdf:resource="LIT4960Taabbeyo//t:div1"/></rdf:Description><rdf:Description rdf:about="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4960Taabbeyo"><lawd:hasAttestation rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/DSEthiop12"/></rdf:Description><rdf:Description rdf:about="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4960Taabbeyo"><dcterms:isPartOf rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3575Mashaf"/></rdf:Description><rdf:Description rdf:about="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4960Taabbeyo//t:div1"><dcterms:isPartOf rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4960Taabbeyo"/><rdf:type rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/"/><crm:P4_has_time_span><crm:E52_Time-span><crm:P78_is_identified_by>1954</crm:P78_is_identified_by></crm:E52_Time-span></crm:P4_has_time_span></rdf:Description><rdf:Description rdf:about="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4960Taabbeyo/title/t1"><rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/E35_Title"/><rdfs:label>ሰአሊ፡ ለነ፡ ማርያም፡ ሰአሊ፡ ለነ፡ ማርያም፡ ኀበ፡ ወልድኪ፡ ኄር፡ መድኀኔ፡ ዓለም፡</rdfs:label></rdf:Description><rdf:Description rdf:about="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4960Taabbeyo/title/t2"><rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/E35_Title"/><rdfs:label>ተዐብዮ፡ ነፍስየ፡ ለእግዚአብሔር፡</rdfs:label></rdf:Description></rdf:RDF>